ssot__Applicant__dlm.name: Applicant
ssot__Applicant__dlm.description: The Applicant DMO represents an individual or group that's requesting something from an organization, such as a loan or admission to a university.

ssot__Case__dlm.name: Case
ssot__Case__dlm.description: The Case DMO represents support cases based on recorded issues, such as a laptop connectivity problem.

ssot__ContactPointDigitalId__dlm.name: Contact Point Digital ID
ssot__ContactPointDigitalId__dlm.description: The Contact Point Digital ID DMO represents enabling customers to ingest, harmonize, and activate various types of digital identifiers along with their values. This object supports known and anonymous first-party identifiers.

ssot__EngagementAnalysisText__dlm.name: Engagement Analysis Text
ssot__EngagementAnalysisText__dlm.description: The Engagement Analysis Text DMO represents a part of an engagement session being analyzed, such as a set of chat messages between an agent and customer.

ssot__FinancialApplication__dlm.name: Financial Application
ssot__FinancialApplication__dlm.description: The Financial Application DMO represents standard data entry structure used to request something for financial purposes, such as a loan.

ssot__FinancialApplicationItem__dlm.name: Financial Application Item
ssot__FinancialApplicationItem__dlm.description: The Financial Application Item DMO represents an item in an application and its related financial product and attributes.

ssot__FinancialGoalFunding__dlm.name: Financial Goal Funding
ssot__FinancialGoalFunding__dlm.description: The Financial Goal Funding DMO represents a financial goal of an individual or person account that requires funding.

ssot__FinancialPlan__dlm.name: Financial Plan
ssot__FinancialPlan__dlm.description: The Financial Plan DMO represents a financial plan for a person account.

ssot__MasterProduct__dlm.name: Master Product
ssot__MasterProduct__dlm.description: The Master Product DMO represents data about a company's products.

ssot__PartyExpense__dlm.name: Party Expense
ssot__PartyExpense__dlm.description: The Party Expense DMO represents the expense incurred by an individual or account.

ssot__PartyIncome__dlm.name: Party Income
ssot__PartyIncome__dlm.description: The Party Income DMO represents the income of an individual or a business. Income can come from salaries, commissions, fees, or rental properties.

ssot__PaymentMethod__dlm.name: Payment Method
ssot__PaymentMethod__dlm.description: The Payment Method DMO represents the way a customer pays for a transaction.

ssot__AccountContact__dlm.name: Account Contact
ssot__AccountContact__dlm.description: The Account Contact DMO represents an individual who has a role specific to an account.

ssot__Account__dlm.name: Account
ssot__Account__dlm.description: The Account DMO represents how a party wants to interact with your company.

ssot__Affiliation__dlm.name: Affiliation
ssot__Affiliation__dlm.description: The Affiliation DMO represents affiliation or how to map Marketing Cloud Engagement business unit use case data.

ssot__AgentServicePresence__dlm.name: Agent Service Presence
ssot__AgentServicePresence__dlm.description: The Agent Service Presence DMO represents a user's real-time presence status.

ssot__AgentWorkSkill__dlm.name: Agent Work Skill
ssot__AgentWorkSkill__dlm.description: The Agent Work Skill DMO represents a skill that's used to route a work assignment to an agent.

ssot__AgentWork__dlm.name: Agent Work
ssot__AgentWork__dlm.description: The Agent Work DMO represents a work assignment that's been routed to an agent.

ssot__AssetServiceLevelObjectiveConseque.name: Asset Service Level Objective Consequence
ssot__AssetServiceLevelObjectiveConseque.description: The Asset Service Level Objective (SLO) Consequence DMO represents network communications data that's sent over a network when the SLO isn't met. These are computer networks or telecommunications networks that include all data packets sent and received over a network, such as emails, voice calls, video streaming, web browsing, or any other type of data transfer.

ssot__AssetServiceLevelObjective__dlm.name: Asset Service Level Objective
ssot__AssetServiceLevelObjective__dlm.description: The Asset Service Level Objective (SLO) DMO represents SLO data that's transmitted over a network, such as a computer network or a telecommunications network. SLO data stores details, such as source and destination IP addresses, timestamps, and data types (for example, TCP and UDP).

ssot__AuthorizationFormConsent__dlm.name: Authorization Form Consent
ssot__AuthorizationFormConsent__dlm.description: The Authorization Form Consent DMO represents capturing where, when, and how a party gives consent for a form, a set of terms and conditions, or a privacy policy.

ssot__AuthorizationFormDataUse__dlm.name: Authorization Form Data Use
ssot__AuthorizationFormDataUse__dlm.description: The Authorization Form Data Use DMO represents the data uses consented to in an authorization form.

ssot__AuthorizationFormText__dlm.name: Authorization Form Text
ssot__AuthorizationFormText__dlm.description: The Authorization Form Text DMO represents an authorization form's text and language settings.

ssot__AuthorizationForm__dlm.name: Authorization Form
ssot__AuthorizationForm__dlm.description: The Authorization Form DMO represents a set of terms and conditions, such as a privacy policy, a contract, or consent forms.

ssot__BenefitAction__dlm.name: Benefit Action
ssot__BenefitAction__dlm.description: The Benefit Action DMO represents actions triggered when a program benefit is assigned to a loyalty program member.

ssot__BenefitType__dlm.name: Benefit Type
ssot__BenefitType__dlm.description: The Benefit Type DMO represents the types of benefits of a loyalty program, such as healthcare, financial, and loyalty.

ssot__Brand__dlm.name: Brand
ssot__Brand__dlm.description: The Brand DMO represents the product's brand, such as Northern Trail Outfitters.

ssot__CardAccount__dlm.name: Card Account
ssot__CardAccount__dlm.description: The Card Account DMO represents a financial tool offered by a bank as a type of loan, with a line of revolving credit that you can access via your card and your card's account.

ssot__CaseUpdate__dlm.name: Case Update
ssot__CaseUpdate__dlm.description: The Case Update DMO represents historical information about changes made to the associated case.

ssot__CommunicationSubscriptionChannelTy.name: Communication Subscription Channel Type
ssot__CommunicationSubscriptionChannelTy.description: The Communication Subscription Channel Type DMO represents the engagement channel where a customer can be contacted for a communication subscription.

ssot__CommunicationSubscriptionConsent__.name: Communication Subscription Consent
ssot__CommunicationSubscriptionConsent__.description: The Communication Subscription Consent DMO represents a customer's engagement or communication channel preferences.

ssot__CommunicationSubscriptionTiming__d.name: Communication Subscription Timing
ssot__CommunicationSubscriptionTiming__d.description: The Communication Subscription Timing DMO represents a customer's timing preferences for receiving a communication subscription.

ssot__CommunicationSubscription__dlm.name: Communication Subscription
ssot__CommunicationSubscription__dlm.description: The Communication Subscription DMO represents a customer's subscription preferences for a specific communication.

ssot__ConsentAction__dlm.name: Consent Action
ssot__ConsentAction__dlm.description: The Consent Action DMO represents what a user consents to regarding their data, such as data collection or web activity tracking.

ssot__ConsentStatus__dlm.name: Consent Status
ssot__ConsentStatus__dlm.description: The Consent Status DMO represents the status of consent, such as opted in or opted out of data collection.

ssot__ContactPointAddress__dlm.name: Contact Point Address
ssot__ContactPointAddress__dlm.description: The Contact Point Address DMO represents the mailing address of a party.

ssot__ContactPointApp__dlm.name: Contact Point App
ssot__ContactPointApp__dlm.description: The Contact Point App DMO represents the software application of a party on a specific device.

ssot__ContactPointConsent__dlm.name: Contact Point Consent
ssot__ContactPointConsent__dlm.description: The Contact Point Consent DMO represents the consent details for a specific contact point, including the date, method, duration, and whether the party has double opted-in.

ssot__ContactPointEmail__dlm.name: Contact Point Email
ssot__ContactPointEmail__dlm.description: The Contact Point Email DMO represents the email address of a party.

ssot__ContactPointPhone__dlm.name: Contact Point Phone
ssot__ContactPointPhone__dlm.description: The Contact Point Phone DMO represents the phone number of a party.

ssot__ContactPointSocial__dlm.name: Contact Point Social
ssot__ContactPointSocial__dlm.description: The Contact Point Social DMO represents the social media handle for a party, such as @trustednews on Twitter.

ssot__ConvReasonReportSegmentDef__dlm.name: Conversation Reason Report Segment Def
ssot__ConvReasonReportSegmentDef__dlm.description: The Conversation Reason Report Segment Def DMO represents a segment definition of a conversation reason report.

ssot__ConversationEntryTranscriptExcerpt.name: Conversation Entry Transcript Excerpt
ssot__ConversationEntryTranscriptExcerpt.description: The Conversation Entry Transcript Excerpt DMO represents a portion of a transcript from a conversation entry, for example, "I need to cancel my order."

ssot__ConversationReasonCategory__dlm.name: Conversation Reason Category
ssot__ConversationReasonCategory__dlm.description: The Conversation Reason Category DMO represents a grouping of conversation reasons that have the same overall topic. It contains aggregated metrics for the associated conversation reasons, such as order management, payments, and account management.

ssot__ConversationReasonReportDefinition.name: Conversation Reason Report Definition
ssot__ConversationReasonReportDefinition.description: The Conversation Reason Report Definition DMO represents an overview of the conversational data structure, including groups of conversation reasons and excerpts.

ssot__ConversationReason__dlm.name: Conversation Reason
ssot__ConversationReason__dlm.description: The Conversation Reason DMO represents the reason a conversation started. It contains aggregated metrics for excerpts, such as cancel order, update order, and check on order status.

ssot__DataUseLegalBasis__dlm.name: Data Use Legal Basis
ssot__DataUseLegalBasis__dlm.description: The Data Use Legal Basis DMO represents the legal reason for contacting a customer, such as billing or a contract.

ssot__DataUsePurposeConsentAction__dlm.name: Data Use Purpose Consent Action
ssot__DataUsePurposeConsentAction__dlm.description: The Data Use Purpose Consent Action DMO represents an individual's consent preferences for consent actions.

ssot__DataUsePurpose__dlm.name: Data Use Purpose
ssot__DataUsePurpose__dlm.description: The Data Use Purpose DMO represents the purpose of contacting a prospect or customer, such as billing, marketing, or surveys.

ssot__DepositAccount__dlm.name: Deposit Account
ssot__DepositAccount__dlm.description: The Deposit Account DMO represents a subtype of a financial account, such as a savings account.

ssot__DeviceApplicationEngagement__dlm.name: Device Application Engagement
ssot__DeviceApplicationEngagement__dlm.description: The Device Application Engagement DMO represents data about device engagement, such as mobile app usage.

ssot__DeviceApplicationTemplate__dlm.name: Device Application Template
ssot__DeviceApplicationTemplate__dlm.description: The Device Application Template DMO represents a reusable standard format for applications to exchange information between devices.

ssot__Device__dlm.name: Device
ssot__Device__dlm.description: The Device DMO represents a specific electronic unit you want to track signals from, such as a refrigerator, watch, or car.

ssot__EmailEngagement__dlm.name: Email Engagement
ssot__EmailEngagement__dlm.description: The Email Engagement DMO represents data captured from various sources about engagement in the email channel.

ssot__EmailMessage__dlm.name: Email Message
ssot__EmailMessage__dlm.description: The Email Message DMO represents an email message, which can be in SMS or HTML format, and attachments sent or received over the network.

ssot__EmailPublication__dlm.name: Email Publication
ssot__EmailPublication__dlm.description: The Email Publication DMO represents a publication, such as a campaign or an orchestration, used in the email channel.

ssot__EmailTemplate__dlm.name: Email Template
ssot__EmailTemplate__dlm.description: The Email Template DMO represents the standard form of an email message that can be personalized and customized based on a campaign.

ssot__EngagementAnalysisTextDirectFeedba.name: Engagement Analysis Text Direct Feedback
ssot__EngagementAnalysisTextDirectFeedba.description: The Engagement Analysis Text Direct Feedback DMO represents the feedback on a part of an engagement session being analyzed. For example, a user can give a numeric rating of the engagement in a survey.

ssot__EngagementAnalysisTextParticipant_.name: Engagement Analysis Text Participant
ssot__EngagementAnalysisTextParticipant_.description: The Engagement Analysis Text Participant DMO represents the participants involved in an engagement session. For example, an agent and a customer are participants in a chat.

ssot__EngagementAnalysisTextSession__dlm.name: Engagement Analysis Text Session
ssot__EngagementAnalysisTextSession__dlm.description: The Engagement Analysis Text Session DMO represents an engagement session during a particular time period with multiple forms. For example, a chat session, a survey response, and a case can all occur during one customer's session.

ssot__EngagementChannelTypeConsent__dlm.name: Engagement Channel Type Consent
ssot__EngagementChannelTypeConsent__dlm.description: The Engagement Channel Type Consent DMO represents an individual's consent preferences specific to a type of communication, such as email.

ssot__EngagementChannelType__dlm.name: Engagement Channel Type
ssot__EngagementChannelType__dlm.description: The Engagement Channel Type DMO represents the channels supported by individual preferences. For example, individuals can set consent preferences for SMS but not for a phone call.

ssot__EngagementTopic__dlm.name: Engagement Topic
ssot__EngagementTopic__dlm.description: The Engagement Topic DMO represents the topics discussed by a customer and other attendees during an engagement. An engagement can have multiple topics, such as campaigns, promotions, opportunities, and tasks.

ssot__FiancialAccount__dlm.name: Financial Account
ssot__FiancialAccount__dlm.description: The Financial Account DMO represents a financial account held at a financial institution, such as a bank.

ssot__FinancialAccountBalance__dlm.name: Financial Account Balance
ssot__FinancialAccountBalance__dlm.description: The Financial Account Balance DMO represents the types of balances associated with a financial account.

ssot__FinancialAccountFee__dlm.name: Financial Account Fee
ssot__FinancialAccountFee__dlm.description: The Financial Account Fee DMO represents fees associated with a financial account.

ssot__FinancialAccountInterestRate__dlm.name: Financial Account Interest Rate
ssot__FinancialAccountInterestRate__dlm.description: The Financial Account Interest Rate DMO represents the interest rate associated with a financial account.

ssot__FinancialAccountLimit__dlm.name: Financial Account Limit
ssot__FinancialAccountLimit__dlm.description: The Financial Account Limit DMO represents limits associated with a financial account.

ssot__FinancialAccountParty__dlm.name: Financial Account Party
ssot__FinancialAccountParty__dlm.description: The Financial Account Party DMO represents the role of an organization account or person account related to a financial account.

ssot__FinancialAccountTransaction__dlm.name: Financial Account Transaction
ssot__FinancialAccountTransaction__dlm.description: The Financial Account Transaction DMO represents the transactions related to a financial account, such as credit or debit.

ssot__FinancialApplicationItemProposal__.name: Financial Application Item Proposal
ssot__FinancialApplicationItemProposal__.description: The Financial Application Item Proposal DMO represents the terms attached to the scheme to sanction a loan.

ssot__FinancialCustomer__dlm.name: Financial Customer
ssot__FinancialCustomer__dlm.description: The Financial Customer DMO represents an extension of an account to capture financial services attributes.

ssot__FinancialGoalParty__dlm.name: Financial Goal Party
ssot__FinancialGoalParty__dlm.description: The Financial Goal Party DMO represents an association between a financial goal with a related party.

ssot__FinancialGoal__dlm.name: Financial Goal
ssot__FinancialGoal__dlm.description: The Financial Goal DMO represents an amount of money needed to achieve a financial goal, such as education or a home purchase.

ssot__FinancialHolding__dlm.name: Financial Holding
ssot__FinancialHolding__dlm.description: The Financial Holding DMO represents the financial holdings associated with an account or a financial account.

ssot__FinancialSecurity__dlm.name: Financial Security
ssot__FinancialSecurity__dlm.description: The Financial Security DMO represents a financial holding in relation to an account or a financial account, such as securities, bonds, or mutual funds.

ssot__FlowElementRun__dlm.name: Flow Element Run
ssot__FlowElementRun__dlm.description: The Flow Element Run DMO represents the status of a single element executed within a flow run.

ssot__FlowElement__dlm.name: Flow Element
ssot__FlowElement__dlm.description: The Flow Element DMO represents the details about a single element within a flow version.

ssot__FlowRun__dlm.name: Flow Run
ssot__FlowRun__dlm.description: The Flow Run DMO represents the details about a single execution of a flow.

ssot__FlowVersionOccurrence__dlm.name: Flow Version Occurrence
ssot__FlowVersionOccurrence__dlm.description: The Flow Version Occurrence DMO represents an instance of a recurring flow that runs on a schedule. For example, a flow runs weekly on Wednesdays and creates an occurrence each time it runs.

ssot__FlowVersion__dlm.name: Flow Version
ssot__FlowVersion__dlm.description: The Flow Version DMO represents the details about a version of a flow.

ssot__Flow__dlm.name: Flow
ssot__Flow__dlm.description: The Flow DMO represents the details about a flow business process.

ssot__GoodsProduct__dlm.name: Goods Product
ssot__GoodsProduct__dlm.description: The Goods Product DMO represents a specific product, such as a carton of milk or a set of towels.

ssot__Individual__dlm.name: Individual
ssot__Individual__dlm.description: The Individual DMO represents contacts, customers, or other people interested in your company's products or services.

ssot__InsurancePolicy__dlm.name: Insurance Policy
ssot__InsurancePolicy__dlm.description: The Insurance Policy DMO represents an insurance policy, such as home or life.

ssot__InterestTagDefinition__dlm.name: Interest Tag Definition
ssot__InterestTagDefinition__dlm.description: The Interest Tag Definition DMO represents products, services, and features that a party has expressed interest in.

ssot__InvestmentAccount__dlm.name: Investment Account
ssot__InvestmentAccount__dlm.description: The Investment Account DMO represents a type of a financial account, such as a brokerage, an investment, or retirement accounts.

ssot__KnowledgeArticleEngagement__dlm.name: Knowledge Article Engagement
ssot__KnowledgeArticleEngagement__dlm.description: The Knowledge Article Engagement DMO represents user engagement details related to a knowledge article.

ssot__Lead__dlm.name: Lead
ssot__Lead__dlm.description: The Lead DMO represents a person or company that shows interest in another company's products or services.

ssot__LoanAccount__dlm.name: Loan Account
ssot__LoanAccount__dlm.description: The Loan Account DMO represents a type of a financial account that's used for loans.

ssot__LoyaltyBenefitType__dlm.name: Loyalty Benefit Type
ssot__LoyaltyBenefitType__dlm.description: The Loyalty Benefit Type DMO represents the type of loyalty benefit, such as rewards or gift cards.

ssot__LoyaltyBenefit__dlm.name: Loyalty Benefit
ssot__LoyaltyBenefit__dlm.description: The Loyalty Benefit DMO represents a perk or enhacement that's available to members of a loyalty program, such as waived airline baggage fees, complimentary hotel stays, or a rental car upgrade.

ssot__LoyaltyJournalSubtype__dlm.name: Loyalty Journal Subtype
ssot__LoyaltyJournalSubtype__dlm.description: The Loyalty Journal Subtype DMO represents a subtype of a loyalty journal type, such as a watched video or product review.

ssot__LoyaltyJournalType__dlm.name: Loyalty Journal Type
ssot__LoyaltyJournalType__dlm.description: The Loyalty Journal Type DMO represents the type of loyalty journal, such as accrual, redemption, signup, or expiration.

ssot__LoyaltyLedger__dlm.name: Loyalty Ledger
ssot__LoyaltyLedger__dlm.description: The Loyalty Ledger DMO represents the points credited or debited for a loyalty program member across various transactions.

ssot__LoyaltyMemberCurrency__dlm.name: Loyalty Member Currency
ssot__LoyaltyMemberCurrency__dlm.description: The Loyalty Member Currency DMO represents the value a loyalty member selects to receive, such as airline miles or points.

ssot__LoyaltyMemberTier__dlm.name: Loyalty Member Tier
ssot__LoyaltyMemberTier__dlm.description: The Loyalty Member Tier DMO represents the benefit tier within the program that a member is assigned to.

ssot__LoyaltyPartnerProduct__dlm.name: Loyalty Partner Product
ssot__LoyaltyPartnerProduct__dlm.description: The Loyalty Partner Product DMO represents a product offered by a loyalty program partner, such as a coupon from another company.

ssot__LoyaltyProgramCurrency__dlm.name: Loyalty Program Currency
ssot__LoyaltyProgramCurrency__dlm.description: The Loyalty Program Currency DMO represents the value or currency that the loyalty program offers to customers.

ssot__LoyaltyProgramMemberPromotion__dlm.name: Loyalty Program Member Promotion
ssot__LoyaltyProgramMemberPromotion__dlm.description: The Loyalty Program Member Promotion DMO represents a promotion that's available to a loyalty program member. For example, a loyalty program allows double points on outdoor furniture purchases.

ssot__LoyaltyProgramMember__dlm.name: Loyalty Program Member
ssot__LoyaltyProgramMember__dlm.description: The Loyalty Program Member DMO represents a person who has joined a loyalty program.

ssot__LoyaltyProgramPartner__dlm.name: Loyalty Program Partner
ssot__LoyaltyProgramPartner__dlm.description: The Loyalty Program Partner DMO represents companies with loyalty program offerings.

ssot__LoyaltyProgram__dlm.name: Loyalty Program
ssot__LoyaltyProgram__dlm.description: The Loyalty Program DMO represents a strategy designed to encourage customers to remain loyal to the business associated with the program.

ssot__LoyaltyTierBenefit__dlm.name: Loyalty Tier Benefit
ssot__LoyaltyTierBenefit__dlm.description: The Loyalty Tier Benefit DMO represents a benefit that's available in a specific loyalty member tier.

ssot__LoyaltyTierGroup__dlm.name: Loyalty Tier Group
ssot__LoyaltyTierGroup__dlm.description: The Loyalty Tier Group DMO represents loyalty programs that have multiple tiers of benefits. Tiers can be organized based on objectives, such as lifetime, marketing, or regular.

ssot__LoyaltyTier__dlm.name: Loyalty Tier
ssot__LoyaltyTier__dlm.description: The Loyalty Tier DMO represents a level in a loyalty program, where members receive better benefits as they move up the hierarchy.

ssot__LoyaltyTransactionJournal__dlm.name: Loyalty Transaction Journal
ssot__LoyaltyTransactionJournal__dlm.description: The Loyalty Transaction Journal DMO represents a collection of transactions related to a loyalty program.

ssot__MarketJourneyActivity__dlm.name: Market Journey Activity
ssot__MarketJourneyActivity__dlm.description: The Market Journey Activity DMO represents a step or activity within a journey in Salesforce Journey Builder.

ssot__MarketSegment__dlm.name: Market Segment
ssot__MarketSegment__dlm.description: The Market Segment DMO represents the grouping of people who share one or more common characteristics for marketing purposes.

ssot__MemberBenefit__dlm.name: Member Benefit
ssot__MemberBenefit__dlm.description: The Member Benefit DMO represents a benefit that's available within a loyalty program that a member qualifies for and has elected to receive.

ssot__MessageEngagement__dlm.name: Message Engagement
ssot__MessageEngagement__dlm.description: The Message Engagement DMO represents a user's engagement with a marketing message.

ssot__NetworkUsage__dlm.name: Network Usage
ssot__NetworkUsage__dlm.description: The Network Usage DMO represents data that's transmitted over a network, such as a computer network or a telecommunications network. Network communications data stores details, such as source and destination IP addresses, timestamps, and data types (for example, TCP and UDP).

ssot__OperatingHours__dlm.name: Operating Hours
ssot__OperatingHours__dlm.description: The Operating Hours DMO represents the availability of a business or business function.

ssot__OpportunityProduct__dlm.name: Opportunity Product
ssot__OpportunityProduct__dlm.description: The Opportunity Product DMO represents a specific product or service being purchased and delivered to the client or prospect.

ssot__Opportunity__dlm.name: Opportunity
ssot__Opportunity__dlm.description: The Opportunity DMO represents deals or sales that are in progress.

ssot__OrderDeliveryMethod__dlm.name: Order Delivery Method
ssot__OrderDeliveryMethod__dlm.description: The Order Delivery Method DMO represents the order and delivery methods for products or service fulfillment.

ssot__PartyConsent__dlm.name: Party Consent
ssot__PartyConsent__dlm.description: The Party Consent DMO represents an individual's consent preferences.

ssot__PartyFinancialAsset__dlm.name: Party Financial Asset
ssot__PartyFinancialAsset__dlm.description: The Party Financial Asset DMO represents a financial asset associated with an individual or an organization, such as owned property.

ssot__PartyFinancialLiability__dlm.name: Party Financial Liability
ssot__PartyFinancialLiability__dlm.description: The Party Financial Liability DMO represents a financial liability associated with an individual or an organization, such as a mortgage or loan.

ssot__PartyIdentification__dlm.name: Party Identification
ssot__PartyIdentification__dlm.description: The Party Identification DMO represents the ways to identify a party, such as a driver's license or a birth certificate.

ssot__PartyInterestTag__dlm.name: Party Interest Tag
ssot__PartyInterestTag__dlm.description: The Party Interest Tag DMO represents the association of a party with an interest tag.

ssot__Party__dlm.name: Party
ssot__Party__dlm.description: The Party DMO represents information about your contacts or clients.

ssot__PersonLifeEvent__dlm.name: Person Life Event
ssot__PersonLifeEvent__dlm.description: The Person Life Event DMO represents a major life event for an individual.

ssot__PrivacyConsentLog__dlm.name: Privacy Consent Log
ssot__PrivacyConsentLog__dlm.description: The Privacy Consent Log DMO represents information about a user's requested consent and privacy information.

ssot__ProductBrowseEngagement__dlm.name: Product Browse Engagement
ssot__ProductBrowseEngagement__dlm.description: The Product Browse Engagement DMO represents data captured from a user action, such as searching for products or viewing a list of products.

ssot__ProductCatalogCategory__dlm.name: Product Catalog Category
ssot__ProductCatalogCategory__dlm.description: The Product Catalog Category DMO represents a category of a product catalog, such as shoes, trucks, or housewares.

ssot__ProductCatalog__dlm.name: Product Catalog
ssot__ProductCatalog__dlm.description: The Product Catalog DMO represents a company's inventory or merchandising catalog.

ssot__ProductCategoryProduct__dlm.name: Product Category Product
ssot__ProductCategoryProduct__dlm.description: The Product Category Product DMO represents assigning products to categories. For example, you can identify that a specific shoe belongs to the running category.

ssot__ProductCategory__dlm.name: Product Category
ssot__ProductCategory__dlm.description: The Product Category DMO represents the types of products a company offers, such as shoes or cleaning services.

ssot__ProductOrderEngagement__dlm.name: Product Order Engagement
ssot__ProductOrderEngagement__dlm.description: The Product Order Engagement DMO represents a user's online shopping order data.

ssot__PromotionLoyaltyPartnerProduct__dl.name: Promotion Loyalty Partner Product
ssot__PromotionLoyaltyPartnerProduct__dl.description: The Promotion Loyalty Partner Product DMO represents the promotion of a product that a partner is co-marketing to loyalty program members.

ssot__Promotion__dlm.name: Promotion
ssot__Promotion__dlm.description: The Promotion DMO represents loyalty promotion details, such as the type of promotion.

ssot__RecordAlert__dlm.name: Record Alert
ssot__RecordAlert__dlm.description: The Record Alert DMO represents the alerts for an account.

ssot__SMSPublication__dlm.name: SMS Publication
ssot__SMSPublication__dlm.description: The SMS Publication DMO represents the process that sends out a set of text (SMS) messages to multiple recipients.

ssot__SMSTemplate__dlm.name: SMS Template
ssot__SMSTemplate__dlm.description: The SMS Template DMO represents a reusable, standard format for text (SMS) messages.

ssot__SalesOrderProduct__dlm.name: Sales Order Product
ssot__SalesOrderProduct__dlm.description: The Sales Order Product DMO represents a product or service being sold to the customer as part of a sales order.

ssot__SalesOrder__dlm.name: Sales Order
ssot__SalesOrder__dlm.description: The Sales Order DMO represents current and pending sales orders.

ssot__SalesStore__dlm.name: Sales Store
ssot__SalesStore__dlm.description: The Sales Store DMO represents a retail establishment where items are sold to the public.

ssot__ServicePresenceStatus__dlm.name: Service Presence Status
ssot__ServicePresenceStatus__dlm.description: The Service Presence Status DMO represents a status that can be assigned to a service channel, such as available for leads, out for lunch, or busy.

ssot__ShoppingCartEngagement__dlm.name: Shopping Cart Engagement
ssot__ShoppingCartEngagement__dlm.description: The Shopping Cart Engagement DMO represents data captured from user actions, such as adding and removing items from a shopping cart.

ssot__ShoppingCartEventType__dlm.name: Shopping Cart Event Type
ssot__ShoppingCartEventType__dlm.description: The Shopping Cart Event Type DMO represents a customer interaction with a shopping cart on a commerce site.

ssot__ShoppingCartProductEngagement__dlm.name: Shopping Cart Product Engagement
ssot__ShoppingCartProductEngagement__dlm.description: The Shopping Cart Product Engagement DMO represents data captured from user actions, such as adding and removing items from a shopping cart.

ssot__Skill__dlm.name: Skill
ssot__Skill__dlm.description: The Skill DMO represents the proficiency, competence, or expertise an employee has, which is valuable to the organization's mission.

ssot__SoftwareApplication__dlm.name: Software Application
ssot__SoftwareApplication__dlm.description: The Software Application DMO represents a program or group of programs designed for end users, such as a shopping application, and the associated permission settings.

ssot__SurveyInvitation__dlm.name: Survey Invitation
ssot__SurveyInvitation__dlm.description: The Survey Invitation DMO represents an invitation sent to a participant to complete a survey.

ssot__SurveyQuestionResponse__dlm.name: Survey Question Response
ssot__SurveyQuestionResponse__dlm.description: The Survey Question Response DMO represents a participant's answer to a specific question.

ssot__SurveyQuestionSection__dlm.name: Survey Question Section
